![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578522323929-WLRP3FV94HMCHSWAU2W5/image-asset.jpeg)

Despite Slade Wilson's wishes, the TITANS ARE BACK but are they better than ever? Join us as we discuss Titans Season 2, the overall tone of DC Universe's first show, and the choices made this season. We also talk about the British elephant in the room as we discuss Iain Glenn as Bruce Wayne, Jason's exile and Dick's daddy issues! Turn off the classical music, put down the drugs and stop having delusions your adopted father as we talk all things Titans Season 2!  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

